Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:03.97,Default,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,Five princes are in love with you, Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:07.85,Default,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,and they have been coming by \Nfor a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:13.37,Default,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,Why not meet with one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.41,Default,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,I won't make such a decision so lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:19.61,Default,Sasuga Fan A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:23.70,Default,Sasuga Fan A,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's hard to see Chisa{**-san}'s face from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:29.20,Default,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,But I believe their love for you is deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:33.33,Default,Panda (Misato),0,0,0,,In that case, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:36.09,Default,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,What is it, Misao?\NDo you have an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.59,Default,Sasuga Fan A,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see her! She's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:44.34,Default,Panda Fan,0,0,0,,{\i1}Panda{**-san}'s as cute as ever today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:49.85,Default,Panda (Misato),0,0,0,,What if the princess marries\Nwhoever brings her what she desires?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.23,Default,Panda Fan,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's too precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.65,Overlap,Panda (Misato),0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sure the love\Nof all five prices runs deep,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:59.25,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Panda Yanagiba's Sense is the ability\Nto read the minds of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.74,Overlap,Panda (Misato),0,0,0,,{\an8}making it hard to judge them on love alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.24,Overlap,Panda (Misato),0,0,0,,{\an8}So why not choose based\Non something tangible?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:05.74,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's going overboard.\NShe'll be getting a lecture later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:32.56,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.368,413.088)\org(964.368,413.088)\fscy99.662\frx-1.67\fnArial\fs108\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(1200,1)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:50.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(123,926.799)\fnTimes New Roman\fs54\bord3\3c&H4B4B4C&\blur6\fad(770,770)}Our First Play
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:49.53,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm with {\i1}Future Dai Star{\i0},\Nthe magazine that introduces young actors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.19,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{\an8}who represent Japan's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.18,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you for speaking with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:56.77,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'm Kathrina Griebel. It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:03:03.21,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,I hear that your parents back in Germany \Nare renowned World Dai Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:08.03,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,Did they happen to give you any \Nadvice when you joined SIRIUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:12.05,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yes. They told me to make sure \Nthat my performances
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:15.03,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,instill the people of Japan\Nwith hopes and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:19.54,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,Your parents have received the \Nmost prestigious German acting award,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:24.44,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,the Reinhardt Award, three years in a row.\NThey're considered Germany's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.10,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan}, are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.99,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm not mad. I'm just at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.82,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:47.09,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You lost the moment you copied Yae{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.22,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:54.44,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Actors who want to be Dai Stars\N{\i1}don't{\i0} copy other actors' performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:59.74,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But at the same time, I'm not sure we\Ncould have beat Kathrina with our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:02.76,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah, her performance was amazing!{sgt: removed "Kathrina-chan" to avoid awkward linebreak}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.55,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What are you grinning for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.18,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.44,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:11.44,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You have to shine brighter than\Nanyone to become a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:12.52,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:16.24,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Let's outshine the lead with your\Nperformance as Misao, the lady-in-waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.34,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.74,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.71,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:34.42,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kathrina's audition performance...\NHow did it look to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.12,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.27,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You watched it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.92,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Tell me exactly how you felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.09,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.80,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I thought it was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.34,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:52.44,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Her expressions, movements, and the way she \Ndelivered her lines all seemed calculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:55.85,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I thought she could've done \Nthe play then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.30,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:02.73,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,But perfect performances\Nare surprisingly boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.77,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The newcomer performance is drawing near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:13.01,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, you and Kathrina \Nwill participate in rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.36,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:19.37,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Find out who you really are before \Nthis performance is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:22.38,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Who... I really am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:27.31,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,If an actor doesn't truly know themselves,\Nhow could they become anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:35.18,Subtitles,Kathrina's Mother,0,0,0,,I know it's the newcomer performance,\Nbut to think you've already got the leading role...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:39.27,Subtitles,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Well, I am your daughter. What did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.61,Subtitles,Kathrina's Mother,0,0,0,,Are you all right?\NNot pushing yourself too hard, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:47.66,Subtitles,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'm fine, Mama. Don't worry. Bye. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:58.02,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Who I really am... Who am I, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.29,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,532.998)\fay-0.02\fnArial\fs54\b1\bord0\c&HB89DB7&\fad(1840,1)}SIRIUS SENTO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.02,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That's not an easy question to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.81,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is why people go\Non journeys of self-discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.16,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:08.25,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I really felt the awe of youth in that line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.92,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:14.80,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.59,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,How would you describe \Nme in a single phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:23.07,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnTimes New Roman\fs45\c&H321E16&\3c&HBEA595&}Furaijinmon\N2nd Year, Auspicious Day in April
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:18.42,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,An idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:19.41,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.65,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Obsessed with acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.05,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Aw, I guess I'll take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:28.81,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,As for you... You're always so \Ncalm and full of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:31.45,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You have so much that I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.57,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh. You're pretty observant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.83,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,But you get mad real easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.08,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,and your face is {\i1}super{\i0} \Nscary when you're angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.67,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You're the one who makes me angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.16,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,See? You got mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.80,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:49.79,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yummy! It's stuffed with red bean paste!\NI love these ningyo-yaki cakes!
