Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:58.89,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1634.181,358.362)\frz15.54\fnArial\fs30\b1\c&H10223D&\3c&H49DED8&}Flower
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:57.41,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You wear your heart on your sleeve,\Nso you suck at lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.90,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.00,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Also, you get depressed really easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.65,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You're probably right about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.86,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But you're quick to get back on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.86,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's one good thing about me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.21,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:15.76,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Figuring out who you are is pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:21.55,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,It is, but actors need to be able\N to see themselves objectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.64,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Objectively...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.46,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What kind of person do you \Nthink Misao is, Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:31.36,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,She's Princess Kaguya's lady-in-waiting\Nand works hard to support her poor family...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:32.34,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.04,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm asking about who she is on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:41.88,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um, she's serious, smart, \Nloves Princess Kaguya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.23,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:48.04,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Once she puts her mind to something,\Nshe always sees it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.36,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,In that respect, she's just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.60,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.10,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Preparing for a role means knowing yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:59.61,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,knowing the role, figuring out your\Ncommonalities and differences,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.12,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,and closing the gap one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.87,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is our stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.87,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,"All the world's a stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.14,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,and all the men and women merely players!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:12.01,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shakespeare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.23,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:28.24,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I suddenly took your hand (chasing you)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:32.91,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And we searched for our dreams filled \Nwith sunshine through the trees (and ran)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:36.39,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,When we had fun (and laughed)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:41.18,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,It felt as though time had stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:46.37,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Right now is (slightly) special
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:51.95,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I knew that somewhere deep \Ndown (and if it's possible)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:56.24,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I want to (be with you) forever
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:09:00.40,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I really don't want to leave your side
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:05.85,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,When the forget-me-nots bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:11.45,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,The prayer I left with you \Nthat day should bloom, too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.41,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,I (touched) this warmth softly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:20.19,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Wishing that I wouldn't lose it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:23.69,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,But some day (someday for sure)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:26.83,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Even if it doesn't reach (that far off place)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:30.50,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And you're going to take these memories with you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:34.29,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,We can still (just the two of us) hide
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:40.02,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,And make this promise with a pinky swear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:46.07,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.72,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:50.26,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:58.11,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,It'd be so much fun to share \Nthe stage with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.86,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'll always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.03,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.83,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,This is the first real rehearsal \Nfor both of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.38,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,so let's start with Misao's entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.56,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.63,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you for having me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:20.63,Default,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,I thought you'd be more comfortable \Nwith a girl close to your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.10,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Misao{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.79,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.33,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Misao{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.60,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.02,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Can we stop for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:33.63,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.75,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You totally just smiled now.\NWhat made you think you should smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:41.19,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,U-Um... Just because?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:42.74,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Don't act on "just because"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.70,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Misao is supposed to be thrown by\NPrincess Kaguya's innocence in this scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:50.12,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You smiling changes everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.04,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:56.71,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,If your acting sucks, you're going to drag\Nme down to your level. You need to—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:00.21,Default,Drama Club,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's on its last leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.47,Default,Drama Club,0,0,0,,We should probably change it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:08.61,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hello?! We're in the middle \Nof a rehearsal here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:11.03,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Stop making weird noises! \NIt's throwing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.09,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Okay, one more time from the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.44,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Kokona, you're standing in the wrong place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.89,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Yeesh. Now she's bossing people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.82,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,All right. Like Kathrina said, \Nlet's take it from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.19,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't \Nwant to switch rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:32.17,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1339.936,117.492)\org(1339.926,117.492)\fscx98.651\frz0.684\fry-3.364\fnArial\fs30\b1\xbord3.85\c&H4E595B&\3c&HAFB5A9&}Become a World Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.22,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,We can't relax with her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.69,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.15,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,We need to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.41,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Say, Kathrina{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:40.54,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you for \Nsome advice about my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:44.90,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You need to work on your focus \Nbefore you even think about your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:48.05,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You're a failure as an actor if you\Ndrop character and smile in a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:49.81,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's not what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.71,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... How do I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:55.98,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it\Nwhen I saw your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.56,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:02.74,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Your eyes looked so uneasy.\NLike you were asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.05,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:08.16,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?\NAre you trying to blame my acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.19,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,No! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.25,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Misao is Princess Kaguya's attendant,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.13,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,so to see her lady uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.79,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Just do what you're told!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.99,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,She really does hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.38,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Who cares about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:36.21,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,But Princess Kaguya and Misao\Nare supposed to be like sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.02,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,who trust each other completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:41.02,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You may just have to tough \Nit out at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:45.51,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,The audience at SIRIUS\Ndesires genuine performances
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.24,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,where the actors let their emotions collide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.28,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:54.13,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,If you truly want to be a Dai Star, \Nwhy not strive to be genuine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.17,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Genuine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:13:01.16,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,You don't need to force yourself to go \Nalong with Kathrina{**-san}'s take.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:05.63,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,You should perform in a way \Nthat's true to you, Kokona{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.24,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.68,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.45,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:15.07,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,How can I put on a genuine \Nperformance with Kathrina{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.75,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,There's only one way to break\Na perfectly calculated performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.59,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Believe in the other actor and face \Nthem head-on without running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:28.08,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,You can also save Kathrina{**-san} that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:31.82,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Save... Kathrina{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:36.78,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,The only one who can save an actor\Nis the actor on stage with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.68,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.45,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You've been sneaking around, \Nfollowing me this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:04.73,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.57,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I, um, just wanted \Nto know more about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.77,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:11.97,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Princess Kaguya and Misao are \Nsupposed to be as close as sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:12.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.91,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I think we should learn\N more about each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.02,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:22.17,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You can't even separate yourself from \Nyour role. You're worse than third rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.43,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You're not fit to be an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.51,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.75,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah. Just a bit shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.34,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,But I'm doing this to make our \Nperformance a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:38.02,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.12,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I need to face her head-on without running.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1326.387,388.908)\org(1326.546,388.908)\fscx98.688\fscy99.963\frz-9.628\fry-3.364\fax0.004\fnTimes New Roman\fs36\xbord2.96\ybord3\c&HBCCDA3&\3c&H46494A&}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1287.273,624.546)\frz350.7\fnTimes New Roman\fs30\b1\c&H6C60C4&\3c&HFAFDFA&}Newcomer Performance Today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.37,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.50,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.41,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.68,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I can't wait to be on that stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.41,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.25,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Believe in what you've been doing in \Nrehearsals and give it all you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.53,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thanks, Shizuka{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.82,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Listen, Kathrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.78,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You can't mess up this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.71,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You have to make this a \Nsuccess no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:32.03,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.368,386.907)\org(964.368,386.907)\fscy99.662\frx-1.67\fnArial\fs108\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(1200,1)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:35.61,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,...for you just grows again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:41.59,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,Even if this is but a faint dream\Nthat will one day fade
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:50.80,Lyrics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,May this falling tear melt\Nwith this momentary fragrance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.83,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kathrin's completely \Ncalculated performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.25,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}So far, it really is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.43,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now we're headed into the climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:13.58,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,I have to... go back to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.82,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:17.72,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,On the night of the full moon this month,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.19,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,messengers from the moon will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.44,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.63,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Even if I don't want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.21,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her Sense disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:44.47,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's... my next line?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:47.11,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:51.32,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um... Huh? What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:57.58,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sense that magnifies one's concentration \Ncreates explosive acting skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:02.83,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the gears become misaligned,\Nthat ability becomes very fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.56,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}It breaks like glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.03,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:45.03,Flashback,Niizuma,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only one who can save an actor\Nis the actor on stage with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.00,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:01.78,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Princess, I promised I would protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.65,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.68,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.90,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:22.16,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But they managed to get through \Nby skipping over a whole page.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.59,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,No, it's only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.59,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:28.40,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,We're having electrical troubles,\Nso the platform won't turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.58,Default,Kamiyashiki and Terahara,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:47.86,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Wait... Has that girl always \Nbeen in our troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.65,Default,Shizuka (Moon Messenger),0,0,0,,Princess, please take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.98,Default,Shizuka (Moon Messenger),0,0,0,,I've come to take you back to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:59.49,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,I don't care who you are!\NI won't let you have the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:05.45,Default,Shizuka (Moon Messenger),0,0,0,,Come, Your Highness.\NIt's time to return to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.66,Default,Shizuka (Moon Messenger),0,0,0,,You needn't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:14.47,Default,Shizuka (Moon Messenger),0,0,0,,You need only accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:18.02,Default,Shizuka (Moon Messenger),0,0,0,,Now, let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.60,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.94,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Take me with you! Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:24.78,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:31.78,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's trying this hard to try to make \Nthe performance a success, while I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:37.07,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.13,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't stop here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.80,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:59.25,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Once I don that sash,\NI will forget all that's happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:05.31,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Before that, I'd like to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:07.56,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Misao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:10.72,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Princess, no! I don't want you to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:16.84,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,I had so much fun.\NYou were like a real sister to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.14,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.59,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,I'm so happy I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.35,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.82,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,My sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.67,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,A month has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:01.85,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Tonight, the full moon is \Nhiding behind the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.80,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.24,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:26.26,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,The bamboo blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.49,Default,Kokona (Misao),0,0,0,,truly were beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.74,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.31,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.94,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,What were you doing onstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.25,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.04,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.68,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.78,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:58.24,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I knew it. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.55,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,really do have an interesting Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:40.07,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(952.401,307.599)\fnTimes New Roman\fs60\bord3\3c&H4B4B4C&\blur6}Fourth Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:40.07,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(958.8,709.2)\fnTimes New Roman\fs90\bord3\3c&H4B4B4C&\blur6}Once Upon a Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:38.90,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Next time: "Once Upon a Time."
